VPK-3927 Volk (Russian: Волк; English: Wolf) - tactical high-mobility multipurpose military armoured vehicle, manufactured by the VPK, where VPK stands for initial letters of the Voenno-Promyshlennaya Kompaniya (Russian: Военно-промышленная компания), meaning Military Industrial Company. VPK is a military division of the GAZ group. The Volk family is based on a highly modified GAZ Tigr.
